        "id": "FireFocusPassiveADragonGirlRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Dragon's Focus",
          "description": "This unit cannot be defeated by damage from Burn status effects, and cannot be Stunned. If this unit is burning, this unit has Hold Ground (if this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP).\n\nAdd a Super Himori to the end of allied reinforcements whenever:\n- this unit defeats any number of enemies with an attack while on the battlefield.\n- a non-conjured Fire ally on the battlefield is defeated or sacrificed by any source.\n\nWhenever a Himori ally on the battlefield is defeated or sacrificed by any source (even if Ephemeral), a random burning enemy is Stunned for 100TU. Whenever an ally Himori enters the battlefield from reinforcements, stun a random enemy for 50TU."
        }
